Package: freshtracker
Version: 1.0-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: php8.0, php8.0-sqlite3, apache2 | nginx | lighttpd
Maintainer: Your Name <your.email@domain.com>
Description: Food inventory and expiry tracking system
 FreshTracker is a web-based application for managing food products inventory
 with expiry date monitoring. It provides alerts for soon-to-expire items
 and helps maintain an organized pantry.
 .
 Features:
  * Add, remove and track food products
  * Expiry date monitoring with color-coded alerts
  * SQLite database backend
  * Simple and elegant web interface